            <ul class="service-features" role="list">
              <li><span class="feat-check" aria-hidden="true"></span>Pare-feu applicatif (WAF) Enterprise Cloudflare</li>
              <li><span class="feat-check" aria-hidden="true"></span>Protection DDoS jusqu'à 200 Tbps absorbés</li>
              <li><span class="feat-check" aria-hidden="true"></span>Chiffrement TLS 1.3 & Zero-Trust Network</li>
              <li><span class="feat-check" aria-hidden="true"></span>SIEM & monitoring des menaces en temps réel</li>
