            </div>
            <div class="service-number font-mono" aria-hidden="true">03</div>
            <h3 class="service-title">Pen-Testing Red & Blue Team</h3>
            <p class="service-desc">Nous attaquons nos propres créations — sans relâche — avant que quiconque d'autre ne le fasse. Chaque site livré a survécu à notre équipe offensive.</p>
            <ul class="service-features" role="list">
              <li><span class="feat-check feat-check-red" aria-hidden="true"></span>Tests d'intrusion OWASP Top 10 complets</li>
              <li><span class="feat-check feat-check-red" aria-hidden="true"></span>Fuzzing applicatif & injection SQL/XSS/CSRF</li>
              <li><span class="feat-check feat-check-red" aria-hidden="true"></span>Analyse des dépendances & CVE scanning</li>
              <li><span class="feat-check feat-check-red" aria-hidden="true"></span>Rapport d'audit détaillé & recommandations</li>
              <li><span class="feat-check feat-check-red" aria-hidden="true"></span>Simulation d'attaques APT (Advanced Threats)</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="service-cta">
              <a href="/contact" class="link-arrow" aria-label="Commander un pen-test">Commander un audit <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="service-glow service-glow-red" aria-hidden="true"></div>
